<plot>Chinna (Surya) has a tough time getting married because of his hunchback. Spending most of his time as a phone booth manager, Chinna assists the floundering romance of Priya (Jyothika) and her bellicose boyfriend Kartik (also played by Surya). Chinna meets blind performer Shenbaga (also Jyothika), and his love life starts looking up. In the meantime, a complication in the other romance spills over into Chinna's wonderland.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?428795</url></doc>
